Package info.smart_tools.smartactors.utils.ioc.strategy

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GeneralStrategy
    Strategy which decides what InstanceStrategy to use to get object of target class when got arguments of some classes.
    InstanceStrategy
    Strategy resolving an object using given arguments.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArgMatchingGeneralStrategy
    GeneralStrategy that calls ArgMatchingGeneralStrategy.getInstanceStrategy(StrategyKey) when target class and argument classes match classes defined on initialization.
    CachingStrategy
    GeneralStrategy that caches InstanceStrategy's resolved by another one (called source strategy).
    ContainerStrategy
    GeneralStrategy that uses a list of another strategies.
    StrategyKey
    Object that should be an unique identifier of an InstanceStrategy.
    StrategyPack
    Group of GeneralStrategy's that may be used by an IoC container.
